node.accessibility_caption: Photo by TODAY on May 26, 2020. Image may contain: 13 people, text that says 'Covid-19 TODAY Govt seeks feedback on NDP funpack after calls to scrap it or allow opt out'

node.text: Fun Pack can dont give la.
Scrap it. Save it for the vulnerable.

The survey by Government feedback unit Reach came after some Singaporeans said that it might not be financially prudent to distribute funpacks or hold the fireworks display during this Covid-19 pandemic period. Others also felt that the funpack is not an environmentally friendly option and will lead to more waste.⁣
⁣
The NDP organising committee had said last week that about 1.2 million funpacks, which are typically distributed to those who attend the parade, will be provided to every Singaporean and permanent resident household this year.⁣
⁣
#linkinbio for the full report.⁣
Definitely No fireworks and no fun packs please. We have proven that we can all gather at our windows to sing/celebrate/cheer together :)
What's the 'fun' when we're already drawing from our 'reserves'? Maybe the Gov should just scarp the whole NDP and give the money the people who need it more.
Scrap it ,  save money .

Scrap the fun pack, give the poor or medical frontline workers instead. Celebrating NDP can be where all the neighbours can come along to sing together all the NDP songs, shining torch lights. That itself will have show our solidarity
Should keep the money for better use, donate to the less fortunate or keep it for next NDP and give the fun pack to each household next year.
Would rather it be scraped out and use the money on more beneficial/meaningful things especially during this pandemic/crisis to help those in need
for*
Government use our money fo fireworks? Why not help the locals or other countries with covid bruh
Why not use the funds to provide some form of comfort financially. We got average people with bird brains for ministers!
Scrap it save money it for poor
Scrap the idea.  I don’t mind not getting it
Please consider scrapping it; we are taking our savings to get thru this covid-19 period, prudence is needed.
Why must waste such $ during this Pendamic time frame ? There were more out that that needs This $ for bread n butter 🤬🤬
Allow opt in not opt out . Don’t waste the resources .
Please scrap and use the fund to assist the poor.
Scrap it. Waste of money and manpower. Not environmental friendly too. Use money for better use to help less  fortunate.
Stop it no need to do

Scrap fireworks and scrap fun packs ALL WASTE MONEY... all the money for FIREWORKS AND FUN PACKS can be given to citizens to use it for more meaningful things... JAPAN no longer does fireworks because it’s harmful for the environment and waste money. Singapore should adopt this
I hope the government hears this!!! We don’t need to waste resources and electricity for NATIONAL DAY!!! For raya, they turn on the lights at geylang which was ALSO a huge redundancy n WASTE OF MONEY
It a wasted to hv fun pack. How many ppl really use it. 🤔
Its just a waste.
I dont need it. Save it for better use.
Can't spell funpack without fun, can you?
Fun Pack can dont give la.
Scrap it. Save it for the vulnerable.
